<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Brandvalley — The UK's Performance UGC Marketplace</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Brands pay per view. Creators earn per view. The UK's first performance-only UGC marketplace — no flat fees, no guesswork, just results.">
    <meta property="og:title" content="Brandvalley — Brands pay per view. Creators earn per view.">
    <meta property="og:description" content="The UK's first performance-only UGC marketplace. Zero upfront cost for brands. Real earnings for creators.">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://brandvalley.co.uk">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            --ink: #0a0a0f;
            --ink-soft: #3a3a4a;
            --cream: #f5f2eb;
            --cream-dark: #ede9df;
            --gold: #c9a84c;
            --gold-light: #e8c97a;
            --purple: #2d1f6e;
            --purple-mid: #4a35a8;
            --purple-light: #7c6fd4;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --border: rgba(10,10,15,0.1);
        }

        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

        body {
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
            background: var(--cream);
            color: var(--ink);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        /* ── NAV ── */
        nav {
            position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 100;
            padding: 0 40px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
            height: 64px;
            background: transparent;
            transition: background 0.3s, border-bottom 0.3s;
        }
        nav.scrolled {
            background: rgba(245,242,235,0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .nav-logo {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--ink); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        .nav-logo span { color: var(--purple-mid); }
        .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; }
        .nav-btn {
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;
            padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; border: none;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .nav-btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--ink); border: 1.5px solid var(--border); }
        .nav-btn-ghost:hover { background: var(--cream-dark); }
        .nav-btn-solid { background: var(--purple); color: var(--white); }
        .nav-btn-solid:hover { background: var(--purple-mid); transform: translateY(-1px); }

        /* ── HERO ── */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 120px 24px 80px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* decorative background circles */
        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; top: -200px; right: -200px;
            width: 600px; height: 600px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(45,31,110,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .hero::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; bottom: -150px; left: -150px;
            width: 500px; height: 500px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,168,76,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
            background: var(--white);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 100px;
            padding: 6px 16px 6px 8px;
            font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--purple);
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
        }
        .hero-badge-dot {
            width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
            background: #22c55e;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(34,197,94,0.2);
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(34,197,94,0.2); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(34,197,94,0.1); }
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.05;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            color: var(--ink);
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s ease both;
        }
        .hero h1 em {
            font-style: normal;
            color: var(--purple-mid);
            position: relative;
        }
        .hero h1 em::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; bottom: 4px; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
            background: var(--gold);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .hero-sub {
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.2rem);
            color: var(--ink-soft);
            max-width: 560px;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s ease both;
        }

        .hero-ctas {
            display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s ease both;
        }
        .cta-primary {
            background: var(--purple);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .cta-primary:hover { background: var(--purple-mid); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(45,31,110,0.25); }
        .cta-secondary {
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--ink);
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .cta-secondary:hover { background: var(--cream-dark); transform: translateY(-2px); }

        .hero-proof {
            margin-top: 60px;
            font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-soft);
            letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 500;
            animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.4s ease both;
        }
        .hero-proof-logos {
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 32px;
            margin-top: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;
            animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.5s ease both;
        }
        .platform-chip {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
            background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 100px; padding: 7px 16px;
            font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink);
        }
        .platform-chip .dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; }
        .dot-tiktok { background: #010101; }
        .dot-ig { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f09433, #e6683c, #dc2743, #cc2366, #bc1888); }
        .dot-yt { background: #ff0000; }

        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* ── STATS BAR ── */
        .stats-bar {
            background: var(--purple);
            padding: 40px 24px;
        }
        .stats-inner {
            max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 24px; text-align: center;
        }
        .stat-val {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--white); letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        }
        .stat-label { font-size: 12px; color: #a78bfa; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 4px; }

        /* ── SECTION BASE ── */
        .section { padding: 100px 24px; }
        .section-inner { max-width: 1060px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .section-tag {
            font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--gold);
            display: block; margin-bottom: 14px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
            font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--ink);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .section-sub {
            font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--ink-soft);
            line-height: 1.7; max-width: 540px; margin-bottom: 56px;
        }

        /* ── PROBLEM SECTION ── */
        .problem-section { background: var(--ink); }
        .problem-section .section-tag { color: var(--gold); }
        .problem-section .section-title { color: var(--white); }
        .problem-section .section-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
        .problem-grid {
            display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2px; border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .problem-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            padding: 36px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .problem-card:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
        .problem-label {
            font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .problem-label.brand { color: var(--gold); }
        .problem-label.creator { color: var(--purple-light); }
        .problem-card h3 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 800; }
        .problem-card p { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); line-height: 1.7; }

        /* ── HOW IT WORKS ── */
        .how-section { background: var(--cream); }
        .how-tabs {
            display: flex; gap: 0;
            border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 48px; width: fit-content;
        }
        .how-tab {
            padding: 10px 28px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;
            background: transparent; color: var(--ink-soft);
            border: none; cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
        }
        .how-tab.active { background: var(--ink); color: var(--white); }
        .how-tab:first-child { border-right: 1.5px solid var(--border); }

        .how-steps { display: none; }
        .how-steps.active { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 28px; }

        .step-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 14px; padding: 36px;
            position: relative; overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .step-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
        .step-card::before {
            content: attr(data-num);
            position: absolute; top: -10px; right: 16px;
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: 5rem; font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--cream); line-height: 1;
            pointer-events: none; user-select: none;
        }
        .step-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .step-card h3 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .step-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.7; }

        /* ── WHY SECTION ── */
        .why-section { background: var(--cream-dark); }
        .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
        .why-card {
            background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 14px; padding: 32px;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .why-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); }
        .why-icon {
            width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .why-icon-purple { background: #ede9fe; }
        .why-icon-gold   { background: #fef3c7; }
        .why-icon-green  { background: #dcfce7; }
        .why-card h3 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .why-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.7; }

        /* ── COMPLIANCE BANNER ── */
        .compliance-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple) 0%, #1e1060 100%);
            padding: 80px 24px; text-align: center;
        }
        .compliance-banner h2 {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
            font-weight: 800; color: var(--white);
            margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        .compliance-banner p { font-size: 1rem; color: #c4b5fd; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.7; }
        .compliance-tags { display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 28px; }
        .compliance-tag {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            color: var(--white); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;
            padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 100px;
        }

        /* ── WAITLIST ── */
        .waitlist-section { background: var(--cream); padding: 100px 24px; }
        .waitlist-box {
            max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto;
            background: var(--white);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 20px; padding: 48px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
        }
        .waitlist-box h2 {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 6px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        .waitlist-box p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 28px; line-height: 1.6; }

        .role-toggle {
            display: flex; background: var(--cream);
            border-radius: 8px; padding: 4px; margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .role-toggle input[type="radio"] { display: none; }
        .role-toggle label {
            flex: 1; text-align: center;
            padding: 9px; border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink-soft);
            cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; margin: 0; display: block;
        }
        .role-toggle input[type="radio"]:checked + label {
            background: var(--white); color: var(--ink);
            box-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .form-field { margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .form-field label { display: block; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .form-field input {
            width: 100%; padding: 11px 14px;
            border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--ink); outline: none;
            transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            background: var(--white);
        }
        .form-field input:focus {
            border-color: var(--purple-mid);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(74,53,168,0.12);
        }
        .hidden { display: none; }
        .submit-btn {
            width: 100%; padding: 14px;
            background: var(--purple); color: var(--white);
            border: none; border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer; margin-top: 8px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .submit-btn:hover:not(:disabled) { background: var(--purple-mid); transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(45,31,110,0.3); }
        .submit-btn:disabled { background: #9ca3af; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; }
        .form-note { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 12px; }

        #thank-you { text-align: center; padding: 16px 0; }
        #thank-you .ty-emoji { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        #thank-you h3 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 8px; }
        #thank-you p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.6; }

        /* ── FOOTER ── */
        footer {
            background: var(--ink);
            padding: 40px 24px;
        }
        .footer-inner {
            max-width: 1060px; margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px;
        }
        .footer-logo {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--white); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        .footer-logo span { color: var(--purple-light); }
        footer p { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }
        .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 20px; }
        .footer-links a { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.15s; }
        .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }

        /* ── MOBILE ── */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav { padding: 0 20px; }
            .nav-links .nav-btn-ghost { display: none; }
            .problem-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .how-steps.active { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .stats-inner { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
            .why-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .section { padding: 64px 20px; }
            .waitlist-box { padding: 28px 20px; }
            .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="navbar">
    <a class="nav-logo" href="#">Brand<span>valley</span></a>
    <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#how" class="nav-btn nav-btn-ghost">How it works</a>
        <a href="#waitlist" class="nav-btn nav-btn-solid" onclick="setRole('brand')">Get early access</a>
    </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">
        <span class="hero-badge-dot"></span>
        Now accepting early access — UK only
    </div>
    <h1>
        The smarter way to<br>
        run <em>influencer marketing</em><br>
        in the UK
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
        Brands pay per 1,000 views — not per post, not per follower. Creators earn every time someone watches. No flat fees. No guesswork. No wasted budget.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="#waitlist" class="cta-primary" onclick="setRole('brand')">I'm a Brand — join waitlist</a>
        <a href="#waitlist" class="cta-secondary" onclick="setRole('creator')">I'm a Creator</a>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-proof">Works across all major platforms</p>
    <div class="hero-proof-logos">
        <div class="platform-chip"><span class="dot dot-tiktok"></span>TikTok</div>
        <div class="platform-chip"><span class="dot dot-ig"></span>Instagram Reels</div>
        <div class="platform-chip"><span class="dot dot-yt"></span>YouTube Shorts</div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS -->
<div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stats-inner">
        <div><div class="stat-val">£0</div><div class="stat-label">Upfront brand spend</div></div>
        <div><div class="stat-val">CPM</div><div class="stat-label">Pay per 1,000 real views</div></div>
        <div><div class="stat-val">100%</div><div class="stat-label">ASA compliant by default</div></div>
        <div><div class="stat-val">3×</div><div class="stat-label">Platforms in one dashboard</div></div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- PROBLEM -->
<section class="section problem-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
        <span class="section-tag">The problem we're solving</span>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--white);">Influencer marketing is broken<br>for everyone</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Brands spend thousands on posts that flop. Creators spend hours negotiating deals that go nowhere. There's a better way — and it's already working in the US.</p>
        <div class="problem-grid">
            <div class="problem-card">
                <p class="problem-label brand">For Brands</p>
                <h3>You're paying for promises, not results</h3>
                <p>Traditional influencer marketing charges per post or per follower. A creator with 100k followers might deliver 200 views. You've already paid. There's no refund.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-card">
                <p class="problem-label creator">For Creators</p>
                <h3>You're undervalued unless you're already famous</h3>
                <p>Without 10k+ followers, brands won't talk to you. You spend more time pitching than creating. And when you do land a deal, negotiating a fair rate is exhausting.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-card">
                <p class="problem-label brand">The old model</p>
                <h3>Flat fees with zero accountability</h3>
                <p>Agencies take 30–50% of your budget. Performance is unmeasured. You have no idea if your £5,000 campaign generated £500 or £50,000 in value.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-card">
                <p class="problem-label creator">The reality for micro-creators</p>
                <h3>Great content. No path to income.</h3>
                <p>You make content people love. But without a huge following, there's no clear way to monetise. TikTok's creator fund barely covers coffee. Brand deals feel out of reach.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="section how-section" id="how">
    <div class="section-inner">
        <span class="section-tag">How it works</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Simple for both sides</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Brandvalley connects brands who need content with creators who make it — and everyone only wins when views happen.</p>

        <div class="how-tabs">
            <button class="how-tab active" onclick="switchHow('brand', this)">For Brands</button>
            <button class="how-tab" onclick="switchHow('creator', this)">For Creators</button>
        </div>

        <div class="how-steps active" id="how-brand">
            <div class="step-card" data-num="1">
                <div class="step-icon">📋</div>
